Text:
I was on roskilde 20 years ago !  

King Diamond ROCKS !

Tackar...
Såg dom på Roskilde, kanske 93 eller 94,
första gången dom lirade ihop med King Diamond på evigheter.
Höjdarkonsert !!!

Needs a few seeders!

Best Extreme Metal album of the 80s! King and Fate rule!

So gaze into your crystal, and tell me all yooooou seeeeeeeeeeee!
